          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Bistable bacteria</td>
            <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Bacteria that have two alternative stable states of low and high abundance, and unlike bimodal bacteria, the states are able to resist change.</td>
            <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Faith <italic>et al</italic>. (<xref rid="bib32" ref-type="bibr">2013</xref>); Lahti <italic>et al</italic>. (<xref rid="bib71" ref-type="bibr">2014</xref>)</td>
          </tr>
