            <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">The assemblage (collection and combination) of microorganisms present in a defined environment</td>
            <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Marchesi and Ravel (<xref rid="bib85" ref-type="bibr">2015</xref>)</td>
          </tr>
