            <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Paine, Tegner and Johnson (<xref rid="bib96" ref-type="bibr">1998</xref>); Walker <italic>et al</italic>. (<xref rid="bib135" ref-type="bibr">2004</xref>)</td>
